DS001.Name: Alice Johnson
DS001.cv:
Alice Johnson
Senior Data Scientist with 5+ years of experience in statistical modeling, machine learning, and data visualization. Holds a Master's degree in Data Science from Stanford University. Proficient in Python, R, SQL, TensorFlow, and PyTorch. Previously led predictive analytics projects at Google, developing deep learning models for image recognition and natural language processing.
